{"type":"message","id":"bf96f12a","parentId":"4246a0a8","timestamp":"2026-03-01T15:00:14.326Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7446d792ccb446b2bf6eead3","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"pet behavior monitor market size demand problems\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 1971,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3797afdf0be7e9cb\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nPet Wearable Market Size, Share & Growth Analysis [2034]\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"3797afdf0be7e9cb\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.fortunebusinessinsights.com/pet-wearable-market-109856\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0ac637af888598d4\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nIntegration with Emerging Technologies such as IoT-based Devices to Fuel Market Growth · The IoT for pets allows pet owners to remotely monitor, gather health data, track activity, feed, and engage in play with pets even when they are not around. In the case of IoT pet tracking solutions, wearable devices for pets are the prominently used mechanisms. There are several different kinds of wearable solutions that can be used for different purposes and the demand for these devices is increasing.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0ac637af888598d4\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.fortunebusinessinsights.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8f236bdddbcd8758\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSmart Pet Training & Monitoring Devices Market Size, Share and Scope to 2031\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8f236bdddbcd8758\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.insightaceanalytic.com/report/smart-pet-training--monitoring-devices-market/2205\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"af0a769b322e52ea\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHowever, the market growth is hampered by the <strong>high cost of the safety and health of smart pet training &amp; monitoring devices and the product&#x27;s inability to prevent fog in environments with dramatic temperature fluctuations</strong> in the smart pet training ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"af0a769b322e52ea\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.insightaceanalytic.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bf66825ea2ab0c2e\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nPet Market Size, Demand & Industry Trends 2026 to 2036\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bf66825ea2ab0c2e\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.futuremarketinsights.com/reports/pet-market\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4e9d7c2f1e43adc1\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n<strong>Spot the shifts before they hit your P&amp;L</strong>. We track inflection points, adoption curves, pricing moves, and ecosystem plays to show where demand is heading, why it is changing, and what to do next across high-growth markets and disruptive tech ...\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"4e9d7c2f1e43adc1\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"January 24, 2026\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.futuremarketinsights.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2d765e039d7016ba\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDog Socialization & Training Hub: Complete Guide from Puppyhood to Senior Years\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"2d765e039d7016ba\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.wagbar.com/pet-industry-market-analysis-the-complete-guide-to-the-261b-economy\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"62057d18073107cc\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThis led to increased spending on enrichment products, training services, and wellness monitoring. Simultaneously, <strong>demand decreased for some services like long-term boarding while increasing for others like home-based pet sitting</strong>.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"62057d18073107cc\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.wagbar.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"16e8217f91cd0433\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nPet Health Monitoring Devices Market Size, 2025-2035\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"16e8217f91cd0433\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.metatechinsights.com/industry-insights/pet-health-monitoring-devices-market-1125\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"329abc5b58a247cb\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAs such, more pet owners get attracted to these innovative solutions that have improved their ability to monitor and care for their pets effectively; thus, causing a high demand in the market. One challenge that presents a hurdle in this market is the integration of pet health monitoring devices into current veterinary systems. Veterinary clinics have many software systems in place for patient data use, which commonly do not interface easily with newer health monitoring technologies. According to a survey conducted by the American Veterinary Medical Association, some 45% of veterinarians reported problems when they tried to adopt new technologies because of issues with integration.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"329abc5b58a247cb\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.metatechinsights.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"pet behavior monitor market size demand problems","provider":"brave","count":5,"tookMs":1971,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"brave","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3797afdf0be7e9cb\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nPet Wearable Market Size, Share & Growth Analysis [2034]\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"3797afdf0be7e9