{"type":"message","id":"ad526d18","parentId":"6927f1a2","timestamp":"2026-03-01T15:00:22.898Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_7d6213803c434f619daf05a8","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"pet behavior monitor problems with existing products\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 1920,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"51cd4f01793c2df3\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nNEW HIGH-TECH COLLAR MONITORS PET HEALTH AND BEHAVIOR 24/7 | PetPace\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"51cd4f01793c2df3\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://petpace.com/new-high-tech-collar-monitors-pet-health-and-behavior-24-7-2/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8327113867b345b2\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nIf any cause for concern is detected an alert is generated to designated recipients. In addition to the early detection of health issues, the device is excellent for monitoring pets with existing health problems, or those at risk of developing diseases, to evaluate their condition, progress and response to treatment.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"8327113867b345b2\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"September 11, 2025\",\n      \"siteName\": \"petpace.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"050b6a78ce089518\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAdvanced Technologies for Pets Health Monitoring System | Cogniteq\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"050b6a78ce089518\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.cogniteq.com/blog/advanced-technologies-pets-health-monitoring-system\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"26770ceb090bc742\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe digital health sector for pets health is a niche sector that requires builders of products and services to extensively understand users’ needs and pain points to create an intervention that will lead to outcomes that solve those problems/pain points. Cognitec prides itself as a leader in the IoT arm of the digital innovation sector.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"26770ceb090bc742\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"February 21, 2025\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.cogniteq.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0e089c3b92de2be3\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nMaven Pet Health Tracker | 24/7 Monitoring | Pet Smart Collar\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0e089c3b92de2be3\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://maven.pet/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"378c985ee12bd9cf\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nKnow if something’s off with metrics like activity/rest, respiratory rate, heart rate, itch behaviors and (for dogs) water intake. Get valuable tips based on your pet’s unique data - actionable insights for a happier, healthier pet. Be alerted of developing issues early on, so you can stop small problems from becoming big ones.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"378c985ee12bd9cf\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"maven.pet\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"fe79a7650b0e2154\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nBehavior Management Products for Dogs | VCA Animal Hospitals\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"fe79a7650b0e2154\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://vcahospitals.com/know-your-pet/behavior-management-products-for-dogs\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"119c8a209bf3f6c7\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nHome security monitors, motion-activated cameras, and even pet webcams are also available for monitoring and assessment when the dog cannot be supervised. Environmental punishment (or booby traps) may train the dog to stop the inappropriate behavior or to avoid selected sites even in the owner’s absence.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"119c8a209bf3f6c7\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"vcahospitals.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"02c10fc87dff1cf9\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nSmart Devices for Pet Health Monitoring | Ambiq\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"02c10fc87dff1cf9\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://ambiq.com/blog/smart-devices-for-pet-health-monitoring/\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"449f1355e812f24d\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDesigned for both cats and dogs, it continuously monitors and measures their vital signs, including activity, pulse, respiration temperature, and burned calories. It provides a convenient and accurate way to monitor pets with existing medical issues while aiding with preventative care.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"449f1355e812f24d\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"3 weeks ago\",\n      \"siteName\": \"ambiq.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"pet behavior monitor problems with existing products","provider":"brave","count":5,"tookMs":1920,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"brave","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"51cd4f01793c2df3\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nNEW HIGH-TECH COLLAR MONITORS PET HEALTH AND BEHAVIOR 24/7 | PetPace\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"51cd4f01793c2df3\">>>","url":"https://petpace.com/new-high-tech-collar-monitors-pet-health-and-behavior-24-7-2/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8327113867b345b2\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nIf any cause for concern is detected an alert is generated to designated recipients. In addition to the early detection of health issues, the device is excellent for monitoring pets with existing health problems, or those at risk of developing diseases, to evaluate their condition, progress and response to treatment.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"8327113867b345b2\">>>","published":"September 11, 2025","siteName":"petpace.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"050b6a78ce089518\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAdvanced Technologies for Pets Health Monitoring System | Cogniteq\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"050b6a78ce089518\">>>","url":"https://www.cogniteq.com/blog/advanced-technologies-pets-health-monitoring-system","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"26770ceb090bc742\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nThe digital health sector for pets health is a niche sector that requires builders of products and services to extensively understand users’ needs and pain points to create an intervention that will lead to outcomes that solve those problems/pain points. Cognitec prides itself as a leader in the IoT arm of the digital innovation sector.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"26770ceb090bc742\">>>","published":"February 21, 2025","siteName":"www.cogniteq.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"0e089c3b92de2be3\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nMaven Pet Health Tracker | 24/7 Monitoring | Pet Smart Collar\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"0e089c3b92de2be3\">>>","url":"https://maven.pet/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"378c985ee12bd9cf\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nKnow if something’s off with metrics like activity/rest, respiratory rate, heart rate, itch behaviors and (for dogs) water intake. Get valuable tips based on your pet’s unique data - actionable insights for a happier, healthier pet. Be alerted of developing issues early on, so you can stop small problems from becoming big ones.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"378c985ee12bd9cf\">>>","siteName":"maven.pet"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"fe79a7650b0e2154\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nBehavior Management Products for Dogs | VCA Animal Hospitals\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"fe79a7650b0e2154\">>>","url":"https://vcahospitals.com/know-your-pet/behavior-management-products-for-dogs","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"119c8a209bf3f6c7\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nHome security monitors, motion-activated cameras, and even pet webcams are also available for monitoring and assessment when the dog cannot be supervised. Environmental punishment (or booby traps) may train the dog to stop the inappropriate behavior or to avoid selected sites even in the owner’s absence.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"119c8a209bf3f6c7\">>>","siteName":"vcahospitals.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"02c10fc87dff1cf9\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nSmart Devices for Pet Health Monitoring | Ambiq\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"02c10fc87dff1cf9\">>>","url":"https://ambiq.com/blog/smart-devices-for-pet-health-monitoring/","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"449f1355e812f24d\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nDesigned for both cats and dogs, it continuously monitors and measures their vital signs, including activity, pulse, respiration temperature, and burned calories. It provides a convenient and accurate way to monitor pets with existing medical issues while aiding with preventative care.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"449f1355e812f24d\">>>","published":"3 weeks ago","siteName":"ambiq.com"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772377222896}}
