ive USB, better room for future features · 🖥 TFT ST7789 240×240 ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5c0b5a8491181fdc\">>>","siteName":"github.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f9dcd80a5f55780a\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nCat object detection based on XIAO ESP32 - Hackster.io\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f9dcd80a5f55780a\">>>","url":"https://www.hackster.io/user2554752/cat-object-detection-based-on-xiao-esp32-33e87c","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"2d15a177d00786ca\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nIn terms of hardware equipment, <strong>the project needs the XIAO ESP32 S3 development board as the main controller, equipped with a camera module to collect image data of pet cats</strong>. The camera module needs to have high definition and wide field of ...\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"2d15a177d00786ca\">>>","published":"March 26, 2024","siteName":"www.hackster.io"}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772377233058}}
{"type":"message","id":"f8e8395b","parentId":"9a32ea4e","timestamp":"2026-03-01T15:00:35.763Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6c6f28cf7ff9493da56ca76a","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"pet behavior monitoring AI machine learning models ESP32"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":17243,"output":30,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17273,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772377233062}}
{"type":"message","id":"97704d2d","parentId":"f8e8395b","timestamp":"2026-03-01T15:00:36.723Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6c6f28cf7ff9493da56ca76a","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"query\": \"pet behavior monitoring AI machine learning models ESP32\",\n  \"provider\": \"brave\",\n  \"count\": 5,\n  \"tookMs\": 956,\n  \"externalContent\": {\n    \"untrusted\": true,\n    \"source\": \"web_search\",\n    \"provider\": \"brave\",\n    \"wrapped\": true\n  },\n  \"results\": [\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a6cebcec3fa060ab\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nStep-by-step Guide To Deploying A Lightweight Ai Model On Esp32 For Smart Pet Feeder Logic\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"a6cebcec3fa060ab\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.alibaba.com/product-insights/step-by-step-guide-to-deploying-a-lightweight-ai-model-on-esp32-for-smart-pet-feeder-logic.html\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"53d23be0fa6297dd\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nAfter deploying our ESP32-based system, Luna’s feeder began detecting subtle differences: sustained low-amplitude vibrations (licking) versus sharp high-frequency bursts (chewing), plus weight loss curves over 60-second windows. Within 72 hours, the system learned her “snack-and-snooze” pattern—dispensing 15g increments when she returned after napping. Over six weeks, her weight stabilized (+0.1 kg), and owner-reported anxiety behaviors (meowing at the feeder 2+ hours pre-scheduled time) dropped by 83%. Crucially, during a 38-hour regional internet outage, the feeder operated flawlessly—proving edge AI’s reliability where cloud models fail.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"53d23be0fa6297dd\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.alibaba.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f25e545b53e7539f\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nCat object detection based on XIAO ESP32 - Hackster.io\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f25e545b53e7539f\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.hackster.io/user2554752/cat-object-detection-based-on-xiao-esp32-33e87c\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5e00d4fe5f12c38e\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThe pet cat visual recognition detection project based on XIAO ESP32 S3 development board <strong>aims to realize real-time monitoring and analysis of pet cat behavior and characteristics by using deep learning technology and embedded system</strong>.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"5e00d4fe5f12c38e\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"March 26, 2024\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.hackster.io\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"abe1466688b5442c\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\n6 Popular ESP32 AI Applications Using TinyML in 2024\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"abe1466688b5442c\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.dfrobot.com/blog-13902.html\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bfa383901f755b28\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nThese case studies demonstrate how traditional sensor technology can be combined with modern machine learning algorithms to predict potential fault points through continuous data monitoring and analysis, providing effective technical support for predictive maintenance in industrial applications. Figure: Using Sensor or Audio Data for Equipment Predictive Maintenance · In the field of smart home automation, combining TinyML with ESP32 can achieve various innovative applications, such as voice-activated devices and automated pet care systems.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"bfa383901f755b28\\\">>>\",\n      \"published\": \"June 18, 2024\",\n      \"siteName\": \"www.dfrobot.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b39b4ac6e5d87688\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nGitHub - PierceBrandies/PetFeeder: Smart pet feeder using object detection and ESP32-cam\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"b39b4ac6e5d87688\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://github.com/PierceBrandies/PetFeeder\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0678242bb114a087\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nIt includes a Flask-based frontend ... the camera view. <strong>A YOLOv8 object detection model is used to recognise pets, while OpenCV is used to process and display the images and layered detection information</strong>....\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"0678242bb114a087\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"github.com\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"title\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f567e7e2cd438e5d\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nDesign and Implementation of a Multifunctional Desktop Pet Robot Dog Based on Arduino Nano and ESP32-S3 | Springer Nature Link (formerly SpringerLink)\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"f567e7e2cd438e5d\\\">>>\",\n      \"url\": \"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-981-95-2098-5_43\",\n      \"description\": \"\\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c81769379cdde63d\\\">>>\\nSource: Web Search\\n---\\nA novel tri-controller architecture is proposed such that the RP2040 Connect is used to implement IoT, i.e., to monitor the states of <strong>Robot Dog</strong> and send fall alerts to Arduino Cloud through IoT controller.\\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\\\"c81769379cdde63d\\\">>>\",\n      \"siteName\": \"link.springer.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"query":"pet behavior monitoring AI machine learning models ESP32","provider":"brave","count":5,"tookMs":956,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"web_search","provider":"brave","wrapped":true},"results":[{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a6cebcec3fa060ab\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nStep-by-step Guide To Deploying A Lightweight Ai Model On Esp32 For Smart Pet Feeder Logic\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a6cebcec3fa060ab\">>>","url":"https://www.alibaba.com/product-insights/step-by-step-guide-to-deploying-a-lightweight-ai-model-on-esp32-for-smart-pet-feeder-logic.html","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"53d23be0fa6297dd\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nAfter deploying our ESP32-based system, Luna’s feeder began detecting subtle differences: sustained low-amplitude vibrations (licking) versus sharp high-frequency bursts (chewing), plus weight loss curves over 60-second windows. Within 72 hours, the system learned her “snack-and-snooze” pattern—dispensing 15g increments when she returned after napping. Over six weeks, her weight stabilized (+0.1 kg), and owner-reported anxiety behaviors (meowing at the feeder 2+ hours pre-scheduled time) dropped by 83%. Crucially, during a 38-hour regional internet outage, the feeder operated flawlessly—proving edge AI’s reliability where cloud models fail.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"53d23be0fa6297dd\">>>","siteName":"www.alibaba.com"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f25e545b53e7539f\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nCat object detection based on XIAO ESP32 - Hackster.io\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f25e545b53e7539f\">>>","url":"https://www.hackster.io/user2554752/cat-object-detection-based-on-xiao-esp32-33e87c","description":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5e00d4fe5f12c38e\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\nThe pet cat visual recognition detection project based on XIAO ESP32 S3 development board <strong>aims to realize real-time monitoring and analysis of pet cat behavior and characteristics by using deep learning technology and embedded system</strong>.\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"5e00d4fe5f12c38e\">>>","published":"March 26, 2024","siteName":"www.hackster.io"},{"title":"\n<<<EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"abe1466688b5442c\">>>\nSource: Web Search\n---\n6 Popular ESP32 AI Applications Using TinyML in 2024\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"a